    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十月十五日　夜",
      "startTime": 0.6999999881,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 200.00001190000006,
          "startTime": 0.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいまー",
      "startTime": 2.6999998729,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3334604,
          "startTime": 4.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "おっかえり～～～～！！　本日の主役の登場だー！\nさぁまずは身だしなみを……ってすでにキマってる！？",
      "startTime": 11.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "え、あ、髪型のこと？　学校で、美容師さんを\n目指してる子が、アレンジしてくれて……",
      "startTime": 22.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "可愛い～！　じゃあ身だしなみは完璧だね！\nまだ制服だけど～、それも可愛いからいっか！",
      "startTime": 30.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8266.6666667,
          "startTime": 39
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、じゃあみんなで、胴上げしながら\n会場に運ぶよー！　わーっしょい！　わーっしょい！",
      "startTime": 38.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5500.001017199999,
          "startTime": 44.4666676839
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ひぇ！？　持ち上げてもいないのに掛け声掛けないで\nあと一人しかいないし。絶対危ないから持ち上げないで",
      "startTime": 47.933978531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとだ！　まだ芽衣しかいない！\nリビングまでだけど、確かに一人だと危ないかも！",
      "startTime": 55.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "あと、普通は胴上げしながら移動したりしない\nあと、誕生日に胴上げすること自体めずらし過ぎる",
      "startTime": 63.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　じゃあ普通はどういう時にするの？\nおめでたい時にするんだと思ってた！",
      "startTime": 71.4666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "それは合ってるけど……うーん……\n野球で優勝した時、とか？　前にニュースでやってた",
      "startTime": 79.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13566.664123599992,
          "startTime": 92.7666641236
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "分かった！　じゃあまずは野球をすればいいんだね！\nまさに逆転ホームランだよ、雫ちゃん！　お外行こ！",
      "startTime": 88.8999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "め、芽衣ちゃん、嬉しいのは分かるけど落ち着いて！\n道具も持ってないし、何も逆転してない……！",
      "startTime": 97.3000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、何してるの？　早く雫を連れて来て……\n……って、なんで抱きついてるの？",
      "startTime": 105.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に野球しようと思ったんだよ～……って、あれ？\nあ、違う違う、胴上げしてお祝いしようと思ったんだ！",
      "startTime": 111.6333282471,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14500.0137329,
          "startTime": 126.13334198
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "一人で胴上げって、ただのお姫様抱っこになりそうよ？\nでも、映えそうではあるわね。試してみましょう",
      "startTime": 121.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9366.666666600011,
          "startTime": 131.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　だ、大丈夫です、瑠依さんも変なところに\n食いつかないで……！　て、手を回さないで……！",
      "startTime": 129.933336385,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.996948300003,
          "startTime": 133.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、みんな待ってるけど……って、わぁ！？\nさ、三人で何してるの？　ご飯冷めちゃうよ？",
      "startTime": 137.6833231611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "よ……よく分からないけど、歓迎のハグみたいな\nものだと思う。とりあえず、リビング行こっか",
      "startTime": 146.433340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_53_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "（誕生日、昔じゃ考えられないくらい、本当に賑やか……）\n（……ふふ、後でお姉ちゃんに、自慢しちゃおうかな）",
      "startTime": 158.0999847411,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spell-weak-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6066.668701299988,
          "startTime": 164.1666534424
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_telepathy-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7100.0284831999925,
          "startTime": 165.2000132243
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spell-power-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11933.34859219999,
          "startTime": 170.0333333333
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}